<article>
    <h2>You don't need toast for breakfast</h2>
    <h3>Gift it to the sea</h3>
    <p>Every day, seagulls have to fight beak and talon for stray chips on our coasts. Support them with a donation of bread, delivered directly to the welcoming arms of our oceans.</p>
    <p>Each loaf you donate will improve the lives of 10 seagulls, or 2-3 really muscular ones.</p>
        <h4>Where should you put your bread?</h4>
        <label for="ocean">In the ocean</label>
        <input id="ocean" type="checkbox" />
        <label for="sea">In the sea</label>
        <input id="sea" type="checkbox" />
</article>
